---
title: 2R Offline Sync Flow
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant U  as User
    participant FE as Vue Frontend
    participant PD as PouchDB (Local)
    participant LS as localStorage
    participant LV as Laravel API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Create reservation (offline)
    FE->>PD: persist(reservation, synced=false)
    FE->>LS: store token & user
    FE-->>U: Queued — will sync when online

    Note over FE,LV: Network restored

    FE->>LV: POST /api/reservations/sync [batch]
    LV->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    LV->>DB: SELECT overlapping slots (FOR UPDATE)

    alt No conflict
        DB-->>LV: Slot available
        LV->>DB: INSERT reservation (status=confirmed)
        DB-->>LV: id assigned
        LV->>DB: COMMIT
        LV-->>FE: {status: created, id: N}
        FE->>PD: update(synced=true, id=N)
        FE-->>U: Confirmed
    else Conflict detected
        DB-->>LV: Overlap exists
        LV->>DB: ROLLBACK
        LV-->>FE: {status: conflict}
        FE->>PD: update(status=cancelled)
        FE-->>U: Booking conflict — cancelled
    end
